articles.author: Anniek Bao
articles.title: Aussie stocks open higher as investors digest China economic data, await Fed rate verdict - CNBC
articles.description: Several Asia-Pacific markets were closed Monday; Aussie, Taiwan stocks higher on hopes that Fed will kick off the rate-cutting cycle with a 50 basis point cut.
